  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8  \u0bae\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0bc0\u0baa\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The jeep that rammed the motorcycles",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A luxury car rammed into a queue of motorcycles near a petrol station in Kalpitiya.",
        "The police informed that the car which was going to Kalpitiya from Palavi met with an accident and said that there was no loss of life in this accident.",
        "The Kalpitiya police also said that the jeep driver in connection with the incident has been arrested and the jeep has been seized."
      ],
